  "title": "beautician",
  "description": "<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<p>Beauticians are highly skilled service-oriented individuals who provide well-rounded cosmetic services to enhance customer appearance and boost their confidence. They may style hair, apply makeup, and provide hair removal and brow-enhancing treatments. They may also give guidance about proper hair and skin care.</p>\n<p>Beauticians Supervisors are responsible for many aspects of personal care and they must be able to provide this care with understanding, knowledge and courtesy. The following beautician Supervisor job description provides further detail.</p>\n<p><strong>Position Description</strong></p>\n<p>Beauticians provide a wide range of services that include the care of the hair, skin and nails. A beautician’s primary focus is on improving their client’s outward appearance and helping them to feel better about themselves in general.</p>",
